Sãn ka gidgra yĩnga tʋm-tʋmdb nins sẽn tar b "lisãns " laogã la nin-saal yel-sɛgdι wã wɛɛngẽ ra tõe n baoa tʋʋm nins sẽn pʋgdã: kãdẽngã pʋg tʋʋma, laoga la ninsaal yel-sɛgdι wã tʋʋm- noor pʋga.
