5-Ne na-kẽnd kãngã, b tõe n wilga zĩis nins rũm-koasdbã sẽn nõng n be wakat wakatã, tɩ sẽn koosdb raasã pʋsã ne sẽn ba be b raagã pʋgã tõe n wa yals n tõog n koos b rũmsã.
