7-Rɩk noor sẽn na n sõng tɩ b tõog n koos zĩ-bãmba pʋsẽ ( wakat ninsa b sẽn tõe n yals be, zĩiga sẽn na n zã toto, la a yɩlgemdã wɛɛngẽ).
8-Zĩndg kibay kũun na-kẽndr sẽn na n sõng rũm koaasdbã tɩ b paam kibayã.
B tõe n dɩka vaeesgã sẽn maan n na n bãng rũm koaasdbã sẽn yɩt tẽns ninsa pʋgẽ n yɩɩdã sẽn kõ kibay ninsa wã, n kɩt tɩ tẽn-kɩrmsa zãadb me kẽes b toogo , la ba maan b pãng sẽn tõe tɩ kibayã tõog n ta rũms koaasdbã.
